"Artaxo P., Castanho A.D., Yamasoe M.A., Martins J.V., Longo K.M.","Analysis of atmospheric aerosols by PIXE: the importance of real time and complementary measurements",1999,"Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research, Section B: Beam Interactions with Materials and Atoms","150","1-4",,"312","321",,,10.1016/S0168-583X(98)01007-6,"http://www.scopus.com/inward/record.url?eid=2-s2.0-0033515178&partnerID=40&md5=06b3a2b50e089ef89d43eeaa25e9c849","Depto. de Física Aplicada, Inst. Fis. da USP, R. do Matao, T., São Paulo, Brazil","Artaxo, P., Depto. de Física Aplicada, Inst. Fis. da USP, R. do Matao, T., São Paulo, Brazil; Castanho, A.D., Depto. de Física Aplicada, Inst. Fis. da USP, R. do Matao, T., São Paulo, Brazil; Yamasoe, M.A., Depto. de Física Aplicada, Inst. Fis. da USP, R. do Matao, T., São Paulo, Brazil; Martins, J.V., Depto. de Física Aplicada, Inst. Fis. da USP, R. do Matao, T., São Paulo, Brazil; Longo, K.M., Depto. de Física Aplicada, Inst. Fis. da USP, R. do Matao, T., São Paulo, Brazil","An account is given on some applications with the integrated use of Particle-Induced X-ray Emission (PIXE) with some modern techniques. The study of biomass burning in Amazonia is detailed which shows the integrated use of PIXE, ion chromatography, aerosol optical thickness measurements and large-scale air mass trajectories. In urban studies in Sao Paolo and Santiago de Chile, the joint use of PIXE and real time aerosol and trace gas monitors is an example of successful integration of these techniques.",,"Air filters; Air pollution; Atmospheric aerosols; Atmospheric radiation; Charged particles; Climate change; Gases; Nephelometers; Spectrometry; Trace elements; Aethalometers; Differential optical absorption spectroscopy; Inductively coupled plasma mass spectrometry; Ion chromatography; Particle induce X ray emission; Tapered element oscillating microbalance; X ray analysis",,,,,,"Seinfeld, J.H., Pandis, S.N., (1998) Atmospheric Chemistry and Physics, from Air Pollution to Climate Change, , Wiley, New York; Cahill, T.A., (1996) Nucl. Instr. and Meth. B, 109-110, p. 402; Maenhaut, W., (1996) Nucl. Instr. and Meth. B, 109-110, p. 419; Swielicki, E., Puri, S., Hanson, H.C., (1996) Atmos. Environ., 30, p. 2795; Edner, H., Ragnarsson, P., Spannare, S., Svanberg, S., (1993) Appl. Opt., 32, p. 327; Rojas, C.M., Artaxo, P., Grieken, R.V., (1990) Atmos. Environ., 24, p. 227; Artaxo, P., Orsini, C., (1987) Nucl. Instr. and Meth. B, 22, p. 259; (1992) Earthwatch, Urban Air Pollution in Megacities of the World, , Global Environment Monitoring System, UNEP, WHO; Artaxo, P., De Castro W.E., Jr., De Freitas, M., Longo, K.M., In: Applied research on air pollution using nuclear-related analytical techniques (1995) IAEA Publication NAHRES-26, 5 (1), pp. PG5-11; Hopke, P.K., Xie, Y., Raunemaa, T., Biegalski, S., Landsberger, S., Maenhaut, W., Artaxo, P., Cohen, D., (1997) Aerosol Sci. and Technol., 27, p. 726; Feitas, S.R., Longo, K.M., Silva Dias, M.A.F., Artaxo, P., (1997) Annais Da Academia Brasileira de Ciências, 68, p. 193","Artaxo, Paulo; Instituto de Fisica da USP, Sao Paulo, Brazil",,"Crafoord Foundation;The Nobel Committee for Physics;Swedish Royal Academy of Sciences;Swedish Research Council for Engineering Sciences","Elsevier Science Publishers B.V., Amsterdam, Netherlands","Proceedings of the 1998 8th International Conference on PIXE and its Analytical Applications","14 June 1998 through 18 June 1998","Lund, Swed",55267,0168583X,,NIMBE,,"English","Nucl Instrum Methods Phys Res Sect B",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-0033515178
